{"tid":1994840,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如何對付更年期老母","createTime":"2020-04-29T18:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T04:32:56.000Z","uid":238121,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a78c1b7e1ff3d92894acecd259a528d34f265bb","tid":1994840,"uid":238121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T18:38:10.000Z","msg":"當我老母踏入五十歲，唔知喺咪開始更年期，脾氣時好時壞。近依半年嚟情況加劇，基本上每日都撩交嗌。<br />\n我做乜野佢都要管，唔合佢意即刻大吵大鬧。<br />\n我真係DKLM，日日比個癲婆咁鬧法，自己嘅情緒都就快癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n各位究竟有咩方法可以對付更年期老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aef59a10bb79c3c444c83fc4493640bbf3a6d65","tid":1994840,"uid":314785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T18:39:39.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"ef7b1927974e579e311c40cbcf58264616ef7b83","tid":1994840,"uid":4672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T18:40:03.000Z","msg":"搬走"},{"pid":"585d09a5e14d0dbf18baa4d81f0b0274b315fcf3","tid":1994840,"uid":130140,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T18:42:01.000Z","msg":"唔出聲，由佢鬧，完全無視<br />\n一出聲佢只會更激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f334ee604855968864074b312c78cb468220377","tid":1994840,"uid":238121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef7b1927974e579e311c40cbcf58264616ef7b83","tid":1994840,"uid":4672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T18:40:03.000Z","msg":"搬走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T18:42:34.000Z","msg":"比人鬧不孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a0fb783432695ec02e6e79c28dc0f9dc8c6f2b","tid":1994840,"uid":2501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T18:42:52.000Z","msg":"屌柒佢囉 更年期大撚哂？"},{"pid":"188c8d55409bb879b41ef50cedcdfc4115c09b75","tid":1994840,"uid":238121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"585d09a5e14d0dbf18baa4d81f0b0274b315fcf3","tid":1994840,